</div></div></div><div class="anchorable docEntry" id="method_appendheader_0"><div class="docEntryHeader"><code class="inline-code-block"><a href="#method_appendheader_0" class="anchor-link" aria-label="Anchor" tabindex="-1">#</a><a class="font-bold font-lg link" href="../.././http2/~/Http2ServerResponse.prototype.appendHeader">appendHeader</a><span class="font-medium">(<div class="ml-4"><div><span>name<span>: <span>string</span></span></span>,</div><div><span>value<span>: <span><span>string</span><span> | </span><span>string</span>[]</span></span></span>,</div></div>)<span>: <span>void</span></span></span></code> </div><div class="max-w-[75ch]"><div data-color-mode="dark" data-light-theme="light" data-dark-theme="dark" class="markdown-body"><p>Append a single header value to the header object.</p>
